Creator Subhash Kapoor

Directed by Ravindra Gautam

Written by Subhash Kapoor . Nandan Singh. Umashankar Singh

Cast .Huma Qureshi. Amit Sial. Sohum Shah. Dibyendu Bhattacharya. Vineet Kumar. Pramod Pathak. Kani Kusruti. Sushil Pandey. Anuja Sathe. Neha Chauhan

Language Hindi

Producers Naren Kumar. Dimple Kharbanda

Production Ismail Varieties Store.

Certificate 18+

Official site SonyLIV Original

Season 2

Episodes 10
